   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Harpochras, son of Tekton(?), from Kerkesoucha, from Kastor, son of Papontos, from the [village] of Karanis in the Herakleides division. I want to lease for cutting and drying hay from the [arourai] which you cultivate and which formerly belonged to the estate of Germanicus near Kerkesoucha in the same [division so and so much arourai . . .]</ab>
         </div>
